# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Fixed

- Fix performance on loading pictures ~200 or above with each picture size is ~1-2MB.

## [1.0-M1] - 2022-03-30
### Added

- Pictures navigation control (next, previous, beginning, and last) on menubar and toolbar.
- Navigation between pictures using the keyboard right and up for next and left and down for previous.
- Zoom and Pan on the picture.
- Load all pictures from the local machine directory and view the given picture.
- Load all pictures from the local machine directory and view the first picture.
- Viewing a picture from the local machine.
